Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhBV6nv8HaFe3ve6pO6uFgA0&fid=0x0:0xcea71958b4ba9bf9"],"When":"2025-8-17"},{"Name":"Ram Subedi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxxOlWN10xbbdfKEDyJjVF5pQNLGaV02zvmQPapkPBuPXiwQ-Uug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Apollo Life Care is a multi-facility private clinic in the neighborhood, just a few hundred meters from my home. It is run by Hem Raj, a young, energetic, and dynamic individual. The clinic offers various services, including a pharmacy and consultations in internal medicine, gynecology, orthopedics, and ophthalmology. Diagnostic facilities include lab examinations and ultrasounds. The pharmacy provides a wide range of prescription medicines at discounted prices. Additionally, the clinic offers first aid, minor surgery, and management of wounds and minor fractures by competent paramedics. Apollo Life Care has been a great service to the people of Chamati and Banasthali. I frequently visit this clinic for routine checks, including sugar and other biochemistry and pathology examinations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICzupGmaA&fid=0x0:0xcea71958b4ba9bf9"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Sudip Adhikari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHoGunE_bYDdrZ6xn-Frvm8KMec3x6f_rpEWMkjlaFueoTuGCw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best healthcare centre at Kathmandu. The medical team at there  was exceptional. They listened attentively to my concerns, conducted a thorough examination, and explained everything in a clear and understandable manner. I felt confident in their expertise and knew I was in good hands.

Furthermore, the efficiency of the clinic's operations was noteworthy. Despite the busy schedule, I never felt rushed during my appointment, and the wait times were minimal.

One of the most impressive aspects of this pharmacy is how helpful and knowledgeable the staff are. The availability of medicines, efficient service, and responsible handling of prescriptions reflect their strong commitment to healthcare standards. More than just a place to buy medicine, this pharmacy feels like a supportive healthcare partner for the community.

I have gotten my hair colored, trimmed and styled.

My experience with coloring my hair have been nothing but terrible. They are inexperienced and don’t understand the concept of chemicals in the dye. My scalp was burnt and yet they reapplied the same dye again because it wasn’t “dark enough”. I have never been in so much pain in my life from coloring my hair. This was a big red flag for me .

I decided to never get my hair dyed there again but instead get my hair trimmed and styled. I come there very frequently to get a blow out. The way they’ve styled my hair have been inconsistent. Sometimes it’s beautiful sometimes I question why I still go there? The inconsistency in quality of service is disappointing.

IMPORTANT: Their staff receptionist during evening shifts have been very unprofessional. She lacks friendliness and a smile on the face when talking to customers. This is a service, every business should make sure the customer is comfortable with the service and the way staff treat them. This is one of the main reason why stopped going there. There was also this lady who would always style my hair, but she always had an attitude with me. Never smiled, never said hello, never asked what I wanted. These two ladies have been disappointing in their attitudes towards customers. Their lack of customer service SHOWS. (I usually don’t say anything and I have always tipped the store and been nice to everyone, but now I finally need to speak up)

Final tip to this place. Either train your workers to understand the basics of customer service or fire them respectfully. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Abhishek Joshi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVefHwtNDrxJc-r0Qd_ZDbtVcs4Z5hyxMKkwLxNsO7Ij4oS4p9y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Having attended and even organized multiple events at The Plaza, I can confidently say it stands out as one of the finest event venues in the city. From the moment you arrive, the experience is defined by thoughtful planning and exceptional execution. One of the most immediate and appreciated features is the ample, well-organized parking space. With clearly marked separate entry and exit points, traffic flow is managed seamlessly, eliminating the congestion and stress so common at large gatherings. This attention to logistical detail sets the tone for the entire event.
The venue itself is both impressive and versatile. The event space is remarkably spacious, featuring three beautifully designed ballrooms that can be easily combined into two or even one grand hall thanks to retractable walls. This flexibility makes it perfect for events of all sizes, from intimate gatherings to large-scale functions. The modern, elegant aesthetic is complemented by superb lighting and decor, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that feels both luxurious and comfortable. Furthermore, the ample outdoor terrace space provides a fantastic alternative for food catering or mingling, ensuring that even when the indoor space is full, guests are never cramped.
A major highlight is the exceptional food catering. The culinary team consistently delivers high-standard, quality food that exceeds expectations in both presentation and taste. Beyond the food, the venue is maintained in immaculate condition. The restrooms are consistently clean and regularly serviced—a small but significant detail that truly enhances the guest experience.
What truly makes The Plaza exceptional, however, is its highly supportive staff and robust security. The team is professional, attentive, and always ready to assist at a moment’s notice, ensuring that every event runs smoothly from start to finish. Their dedication, combined with the venue’s impeccable design and functionality, makes The Plaza a reliable and outstanding choice for any event. I have thoroughly enjoyed every occasion I’ve attended here and cannot recommend it highly enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhA4xdDp_v3AVm8j0iwI26vm&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-8-31"},{"Name":"Techie Rohit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIYryHC2LYDsTaWVoQSmr5nRiv4OzcYxE5vnN8AukQjuX2vZHXzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place for party. From the very beginning, the venue created a strong impression. The location is convenient, and the parking system is well-managed, with separate entry and exit points that help control traffic flow. The banquet hall itself is lavish, spacious, and beautifully designed. With elegant décor and impressive lighting, the ambiance felt aesthetic and picture-perfect—ideal for photography and special occasions. A thoughtful touch was the provision of a VIP room, where guests could securely store their bags and belongings during the event.

However, the food was average at best. Some dishes became cold over time, and the desserts, though visually appealing, were disappointing in taste. Since it was a cocktail dinner, the bartender and liquor arrangements were managed separately by us.
The service from the staffs was good but I didn't like the way snacks food being served on a Napkin paper with just a toothpick, which I felt very unprofessional for such a venue. The buffet dinner was decent but did not meet the same premium standard as the setting.

On the positive side, the staff were polite and attentive, but the food quality and service style need considerable improvement to match the elegance of the venue.

Overall: The Plaza is a luxurious, well-equipped, and impressive banquet venue, perfectly suited for launches, celebrations, and corporate events. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"global trade solutions and supplyers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6faFQZOIZmnI2aGdUV1pPcpcG7V59ZC5SYugllxEPIEzgIOKn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Acme is the one of many pharmacy shop who can provide all kinds of medicines of different companies from single door. Discount available here minimum 10% depending on medicines you buy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shaurab Lohani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoQVBT3aoV3MOm6FH8n-fS7opsygIjMfiO8K3k_j7PIA4fvgIc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a pharmacy located close to Teaching hospital in Maharajgunj, Kathmandu. This is not in the busiest road and is on the talim kendra junction. The pharmacy has parking available in the adjacent clinic that they operate as well. You can find almost all sorts of prescribed allopathy medicine in this pharmacy. There are around 2-3 attendants at time so the service is quick. In case you do not find the medicines you are looking for you can simple place and order and it should be available at no time. The only downside is the roadside parking if you need some medicines quickly. Since it is in a vip area, most of the time traffic police prohibits from stopping for even seconds.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICklfPMxgE&fid=0x0:0x3e2340edf76c4d71"],"When":"2018-10-24"},{"Name":"Bibek Someone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJU4wDnHyXt2zajfhQJDMSkv-NhUvHKOuKfzxz8Cb_h7jeHMW8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Went there to buy Amip 10 (Amiptriptyline), an antidepressant for a family member and ended up buying Arip 10 used for treating a bipolar disorder!!!! Thank god I double checked once I got back home and then hurried to the pharmacy, with an unapologetic grin, ''You should have known by the price you paid. The difference between the cost of those two drugs  is huge!"

Most people in Nepal just trust the pharmacy and I think very few people double-check. In fact most people do not know how to check if the medicines that they have been handed by the pharmacy is accurate or not. Yes I do know mistakes do happen and to err is human, but when you have taken more than 5 minutes, including a few scroll on the computer screen and when the doctor's handwriting is legible, to make such a mistake for psychotropic medicines is nothing but an utter negligence.

Actually their sheer carelessness warrants a 1 star but I will be a little generous and add more as they are conveniently located and at times provide discounts on medicines, so we're not required to go to pharmacies of the government hospitals to save a few rupees.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgMCIuNmrogE&fid=0x0:0x3e2340edf76c4d71"],"When":"2025-3-30"},{"Name":"Prabin Tiwari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYpYT9sXdCoMdSmKYPAwbUEk8g9uezoyXAh-UZBN8HJKdZRUAc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Acme Pharmacy is an excellent place for all medical needs. They have a wide range of medicines available, ensuring that you can find what you need without hassle. What sets them apart is their superior counseling service—far better than other pharmacies. The staff is knowledgeable, professional, and genuinely helpful, providing clear guidance on medications and usage. Highly recommended for anyone looking for quality service and availability!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nab Raj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf-1vz9od03ygBKdiBoI28eE_vLO8YBBshE86vsUiBYwLj2vqTtw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"You can get 10% discount on every purchase","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ankit Aryal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmtf08bOuHYsA8tV9u9qIF70o-RN4rkxC0syYuZJJDLq3cpPCN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Please be careful while buying medicine here.
We were supposed to get T. Flontin Tabs (Antibiotics) for infection but the pharmasist gave us FolVin which is acid based medicine used in treatment of alzheimier. My wife googled it just randomly and was shocked to find this out.

We later went to another Pharmasist who told us the medicine given to us were completely wrong from.prescribed one.

Its not only aboout good doctors. You need to find good Pharmacy too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aarushi Pandey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfMZzVBVryrndE7db_rf3t8PZQBVgd5Q5WNEVlXv8oc6sloQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"best pharmacy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anishrestha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGuxNM6q-nZSLSv8RhqYfBwpilno2H7jYXTY1fsEdHJZlPTBgk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pharmacy in the Area","Images":null,"When":""}]

The atmosphere of the store is calming and peaceful, filled with the natural aromas of essential oils, herbs, and Ayurvedic products, which set the tone for a healing experience.

The variety of products available is impressive. Whether you're looking for natural remedies for stress, digestive issues, skin health, or immune support, Sahayogi Auyurvedic Pharmacy has a wide selection of high-quality, organic herbs, powders, and oils that cater to different needs. The store carries well-known Ayurvedic brands, as well as unique, lesser-known products that you might not find elsewhere. They have included highly qualified and trained ayurvedic doctors too. During my visit, I was able to consult with one of the doctors who took a thorough approach, asking about my lifestyle, diet, and overall well-being. They provided insightful advice and recommended specific herbs and treatments, helping me feel more aligned with my health goals

I left the pharmacy feeling not only with the products I needed but also with a deeper understanding of how Ayurveda works to support overall health and wellness. I recently had the pleasure of visiting Wave Pharmacy for my healthcare needs, and I must say, I was thoroughly impressed. From start to finish, my experience was nothing short of outstanding.
First and foremost, the staff at Wave Pharmacy were incredibly knowledgeable and courteous. They took the time to understand my requirements and offered personalized recommendations tailored to my needs. Their professionalism and expertise truly set them apart.
Moreover, I was blown away by the wide range of high-quality products available here. Whether it was medications, medical supplies, or wellness products, they had everything I needed under one roof. The products were all from reputable brands and of the highest standards.
Furthermore, the store's cleanliness and organization were impeccable, creating a pleasant for customers. It's evident that Pharmacy prioritizes hygiene and customer comfort.

Additionally, I was pleasantly surprised by the efficiency of their service. Despite the busy nature of the store, I didn't have to wait long to receive assistance, and the checkout process was swift and hassle-free.

Overall, my experience at Wave Pharmacy exceeded my expectations in every aspect. I wholeheartedly recommend this store to anyone in need of top-notch healthcare products and exceptional service. Five stars without a doubt!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Dipesh Tajpuriya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmYPPpfZW13wPDGMe4JPHm0K8oDx8rphmmvnpP-KLixt1wTxNN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yarsagumba, scientifically known as Ophiocordyceps sinensis, is a rare and unique medicinal fungus that grows in the high-altitude regions of the Himalayas, particularly in Nepal, Tibet, Bhutan, and parts of India. It holds significant cultural, economic, and medicinal value in these regions.

Yarsagumba is a parasitic fungus that infects and eventually mummifies the larvae of ghost moths. The fungus grows out of the larva's body, forming a distinctive caterpillar-fungus hybrid structure. This natural phenomenon has been used for centuries in traditional Chinese and Tibetan medicine for its purported health benefits, including boosting energy, enhancing libido, and improving overall well-being.

Due to its scarcity and high demand, yarsagumba has become a valuable commodity, often referred to as the "Himalayan Viagra" or "Himalayan Gold." The harvest season, which typically occurs in late spring and early summer, sees local communities and harvesters combing the alpine meadows in search of this fungus. However, overharvesting and ecological concerns have led to conservation efforts and regulations to ensure sustainable collection.

The trade in yarsagumba has both positive and negative impacts. While it offers economic opportunities for rural communities, it also raises issues of exploitation, unsustainable practices, and conflicts among collectors. Research continues to explore the medicinal properties and ecological implications of yarsagumba, highlighting its significance as a unique and intriguing natural phenomenon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Weblink Nepal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvq6KuEb2mgWVFp8xmhcu7cfpUuLmN_mgvk98RqSt4EnNDmHw7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Boost your immunity","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KbK Dongja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJt8t4BZY9Ux-pmi8HYwJ3gTc0YY2jfI7OywvbtRmv5m--V_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bhoj darai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPYxFOX60FK8PQPsbXVRuRlEegjRpdMcyjnirvBGn8C5QQ9fY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"","Images":null,"When":""}]
